---

<BaseLayout
  title="Budget-Friendly Date Night Restaurants in Los Angeles: Romantic Dining Under $50"
  description="Discover amazing date night restaurants in LA that won't break the bank. These romantic spots offer excellent food and ambiance for under $50 per person."
  keywords={['budget date night Los Angeles', 'cheap romantic restaurants LA', 'affordable date night LA', 'under $50 date night', 'budget dining Los Angeles']}
  canonical="https://datenightrestaurants.com/blog/budget-friendly-date-night-restaurants-los-angeles/"
