                  <h3>üïê Timing is Everything</h3>
                  <p>Many restaurants offer early bird specials, happy hour deals, and weekday discounts. Dining between 5-7 PM or on weekdays can save you 20-30%.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="strategy-card">
                  <h3>üç∑ Share and Save</h3>
                  <p>Order one appetizer to share, split a main course, and share dessert. This approach lets you try more dishes while keeping costs down.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="strategy-card">
                  <h3>üç∏ Happy Hour Dining</h3>
                  <p>Many restaurants offer discounted drinks and appetizers during happy hour. Perfect for a casual date night with great value.</p>
                </div>
                
                <div class="strategy-card">
                  <h3>üåÆ Explore Different Cuisines</h3>
                  <p>Ethnic restaurants often offer incredible value. Try authentic Mexican, Thai, or Middle Eastern cuisine for unique experiences at lower prices.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </section>

            <section class="budget-neighborhoods">
