                  <h3>üåÆ East LA & Boyle Heights</h3>
                  <p>Authentic Mexican cuisine with incredible value. Family-owned restaurants offer generous portions and authentic flavors at budget-friendly prices.</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Authentic Mexican cuisine</li>
                    <li>Generous portions</li>
                    <li>Family-owned restaurants</li>
                    <li>Under $20 per person</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="neighborhood-card">
