                  <p>Korean BBQ and traditional dishes offer great value and unique dining experiences. Many restaurants have all-you-can-eat options.</p>
                  <ul>
                    <li>Korean BBQ experiences</li>
                    <li>All-you-can-eat options</li>
                    <li>Traditional Korean dishes</li>
                    <li>Group-friendly dining</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
                
                <div class="neighborhood-card">
                  <h3>üçù Little Italy</h3>
